{"tid":146882,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟有幾多人搭車嗰陣會放低背囊？","createTime":"2017-03-07T12:49:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-08T08:07:16.000Z","uid":943,"like":259,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0dc98a21f9aa60ae0f60b71086b85086d14504d1","tid":146882,"uid":943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T12:49:01.000Z","msg":"啱啱搭車，眼望四周都唔見有人放低<br />\n我自己都冇呢個習慣<br />\n一嚟地下污糟又會俾人踩到背囊帶<br />\n二嚟可能會有廢老俾袋kick親<br />\n三嚟夾住個背囊好唔舒服<br />\n四嚟拎住又好重，我每日搭港鐵總站搭到總站，拎住真係好攰<br />\n大家又點睇呢？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  正評:唔放，好污糟<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 負皮:放啊，阻住晒其他人出入"},{"pid":"f80f255a101cd4d56e065e5ffc941186dcdac2d8","tid":146882,"uid":72306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T12:50:08.000Z","msg":"從來未見過"},{"pid":"9dab2fbdaf70d5e3ea3eae27d52a62d61d2159aa","tid":146882,"uid":943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T12:51:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>從來未見過</blockquote><br />\n未見過有人放低？我見過，但唔多"},{"pid":"48867b957ac355b60826f8f75dfdbcf345102069","tid":146882,"uid":60508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T12:51:09.000Z","msg":"從來冇放"},{"pid":"02295c25c8d7821c3580d9a3d7a5be8317eec755","tid":146882,"uid":89608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T12:52:25.000Z","msg":"根本就唔係一個解決擠逼既好方法, 唔會理, 不過好快就會因為唔放<br />\n<br />\n背囊而出現一堆爭吵時間, 廢老又多個批鬥年青人既理由"},{"pid":"2bbf6f1649a2f683340bf8dfbfffcf7e8684edaf","tid":146882,"uid":943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T12:52:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>從來冇放</blockquote><br />\n我見有巴打話一定會放，因為阻住人<br />\n一係就話手拎<br />\n但放同手拎我都唔想，可能我自私啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e2f2f6211f72b6e168a1722e7acdd7b28f0a2bd","tid":146882,"uid":943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T12:53:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>根本就唔係一個解決擠逼既好方法, 唔