70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T01:45:08.000Z","msg":"依d係公民意識既野<br />\n跟本地鐵就on99做埋d垃圾提醒<br />\n你入lift多人既時候，都會自動除袋手拎，唔駛教<br />\n地鐵咁撚多人，想除袋都除唔到，放地下比人踩到爛咩<br />\n要講都講拖gip個班先，轆撚死人"},{"pid":"ffef1c90c3f21513690261b9a9ccc141c539d7cd","tid":146882,"uid":36169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T01:46:35.000Z","msg":"如果你放低個LV，我就放低背囊，咁就公平啦，八婆"},{"pid":"dd19c75bc0c8018c1890531b7b9503d916abcae7","tid":146882,"uid":4326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T01:46:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>根本就唔係一個解決擠逼既好方法, 唔會理, 不過好快就會因為唔放<br />\n<br />\n背囊而出現一堆爭吵時間, 廢老又多個批鬥年青人既理由</blockquote><br />\n真啊，多得個垃圾廣告</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n狗鐵關公睇唔睇到呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下次記住拍個廣告醜化班後生唔讓位比廢老<br />\n<br />\n記住整啲讓老十式比班後生仔嘆下"},{"pid":"4519a066f6b48898d48b4ff2ffcdb9d631fab836","tid":146882,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T01:47:54.000Z","msg":"我不嬲都會放低<br />\n但我純粹覺得重先放低<br />\n地鐵個廣告反而令我之後搭車都唔想除低佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0a77f6a4899dfa57b3ec503227bfdedb0fef22a","tid":146882,"uid":54103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T01:49:46.000Z","msg":"袋住電腦點敢放地下，仲要咁撚迫實俾人踼爛"},{"pid":"f902a4b13687e02f7d39b3d7a14d884b11fa2d65","tid":146882,"uid":46548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T01:51:11.000Z","msg":"比起放背囊喺地<br />\n唔好低頭睇睇whatsapp <br />\n收返埋部手提更加實際同有效率"},{"pid":"da7506aa70fdc0dd1a8478d2782307d8af8e2cf0","tid":146882,"uid":58071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T01:54:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c32d06f86fabc2124206418e0087f8c9a81c49d2","tid":146882,